{"tid":1009603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"史上最尷尬時刻","createTime":"2019-02-05T09:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T11:22:05.000Z","uid":158903,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa15364e840b113148666b95b7d5c091ee27452","tid":1009603,"uid":158903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"話說小弟嘅lecturer介紹咗份<br />\n一日part time俾我地班學生<br />\n份pt返三個鐘 就有500蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後我同另外兩個fd就應承咗去做<br />\n<br />\n點知返工前一日 <br />\n個負責人臨時唔洗我地返<br />\n但啲糧會照出俾我地<br />\n仲叫我地俾銀行ac 過數<br />\n小弟呢個時候就秒覆gp俾咗ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知另外兩個fd話：「我地唔要啲錢喇，我地冇做野，唔應該收。」<br />\n<br />\n簡直尷尬到救撚命<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事後個負責人仲通知埋我lecturer <br />\nlecturer 都話人地俾得你收啦 <br />\n佢兩個堅持唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果個負責人pm我過埋數俾我 <br />\n而我成功變咗個貪錢嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [black][/black]"},{"pid":"2d5422f22c424450254def0563f3e26dc9a3d996","tid":1009603,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"462a43324ae1cb2a0ca3a518541f868481fe3ad5","tid":1009603,"uid":3698,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:45:50.000Z","msg":"對家：合約精神<br />\n你：權利<br />\n你朋友：道義立場<br />\n<br />\n三個都無錯<br />\n比左你佢地又唔肯收錢<br />\n咪當係舊錢比左你，你再黎同佢地玩/食左佢<br />\n吞人地果份就唔好喇"},{"pid":"6b7d70398bd10489210d7782ceb047e191a5787d","tid":1009603,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:46:11.000Z","msg":"<sp